ops::bit::BitXor::bitxor.doc:
Performs the `^` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(true ^ false, true);
assert_eq!(true ^ true, false);
assert_eq!(5u8 ^ 1u8, 4);
assert_eq!(5u8 ^ 2u8, 7);
```

src:
fn bitxor(self, rhs: bool) -> Self::Output {
        self ^ Self::splat(rhs)
    }

